com.rhizospherejs.gwt.client.meta
Interface HasLink

public interface HasLink

Interface assigned to an AttributeDescriptor to declare that its matching RhizosphereModelAttribute defines links to other Rhizosphere models.

See RhizosphereMetaModel.Attribute.setLink(boolean).

Author:
battlehorse@google.com (Riccardo Govoni)

Method Detail

isLink

boolean isLink()
Returns whether the model attribute defines a link to other visualization models.

linkKey

java.lang.String linkKey()
Defines the name of the target model attribute whose value resolves the links established by this attribute. If null, it is assumed that the values of model attribute identified by this interface will contain the unique ids of their linked models. If specified, the values of the target model attribute must be unique across all visualization models.

Returns:
the name of the target model attribute whose value resolves the links established by this attribute, or null if this attribute links to other models via their unique ids.
